data.description: Stunning, comfort, elegance & Location describes this ultimate entertainers delight - the place you call home! RARE find....................-- Executive Single Story home with heated pool /spa, Oversized Premium Lot, Full outdoor kitchen w/refrigerator & sink and 6  burner BBQ, mtn views galore 4bed 3.5 bath, SOLAR home that has a rare 4 car GARAGE..!!! Most of the Furnishings can also be sold  / Awesome opportunity for the snow bird, or vacation home!!! Warm interior ambiance / with Chefs kitchen- huge island and ample cabinetry & walk in pantry.  Unique Split floor plan that has a formal dining room & Den that can easily be a 5th BDRM. Great Curb appeal with a Private Courtyard. Easy maintenance landscaping with Premium pavers in the right areas! WOW- Assumable VA Loan 3.25% ! see today Location, Location, Location... This home is in a Nicholas Design Golf Course. This home also has a Tankless hot water system, 6 camera security system and built in outdoor sound system in the backyard. Resort Style community of Estrella Mountain Ranch. All inclusive Estrella amenities include  Lakes, yacht club, fishing (catch and release)  over 50 miles of hiking biking trails, Pickleball / tennis courts, Basketballer courts / Volley Ball courts, & Several kids playgrounds. Enjoy Presidio & Starpoint community centers with Heated Lap pool, outdoor heated pool, and outdoor pool with waterslides. Both community centers also have State of the Art Gym work out facilities. *** Home can also be sold with Furnishings. a possible turn key opportunity!
